l1/zhnb/2015/0323/00/29260139.shtml 韩籍日裔隆大介动粗还叫嚣 电影剧组] {{Wayback|url=http://news.21cn.com/caiji/roll1/zhnb/2015/0323/00/29260139.shtml |date=20160304203240 }}21cn</ref><ref>[http://www.hinews.cn/news/system/2015/03/23/017419797.shtml 韩艺人隆大介发酒疯 机场打断台湾移民官腿] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hinews.cn/news/system/2015/03/23/017419797.shtml |date=20150325175627 }}南海网</ref><ref>[http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20150322001959-260401　韓藝人「隆大介」醉鬧機場 打斷移民關腿] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326010424/http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20150322001959-260401 |date=2015-03-26 }}中時電子網</ref><ref>[http://www.setn.com/E/News.aspx?PageGroupID=8&NewsID=66858 太囂張！韓籍演員隆大介來台拍片　酒醉踹斷移民官腿骨] {{Wayback|url=http://www.setn.com/E/News.aspx?PageGroupID=8&NewsID=66858 |date=20150402182303 }}三立新聞</ref><ref>[http://news.rti.org.tw/news/detail/?recordId=179571 韓星酒醉攻擊移民官影視局：劇組將助賠償] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402095055/http://news.rti.org.tw/news/detail/?recordId=179571 |date=2015-04-02 }}中央廣播電台</ref>。劇組發聲明痛陳：「由於這件不可接受的傷害行為，劇組已即刻停止他在本片的任何演出。」劇組說他在片中僅演小角色，並要他配合警檢調查，負起所有責任。<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://udn.com/news/story/7262/783723-隆大介遭「沉默」開除 |title=隆大介遭「沉默」開除 |publisher=[[世界日報|世界日報]] |date=2015年3月24日 |accessdate=2015-03-24 |archive-date=2015-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150324123635/http://udn.com/news/story/7262/783723-%E9%9A%86%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%8B%E9%81%AD%E3%80%8C%E6%B2%89%E9%BB%98%E3%80%8D%E9%96%8B%E9%99%A4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==發行==
[[馬丁·史柯西斯|馬丁·史柯西斯]]最先於2013年[[坎城影展|坎城影展]]上銷售發行權<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/martin-scorseses-silence-lands-key-560715 |title=Martin Scorsese's 'Silence' Lands Key Foreign Territory Deals |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=March 2, 2014 |archive-date=2014-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321151825/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/martin-scorseses-silence-lands-key-560715 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年7月，[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]收購了電影的美國發行權，並預計於2015年底上映<ref name=deadline201407>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2014/07/paramount-martin-scorsese-silence-803900/ |script-title=en:Paramount Acquiring Martin Scorsese’s ‘Silence’ For 2015 Oscar Season |work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline]] |accessdate=November 14, 2015 |archive-date=2014-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141228204908/http://deadline.com/2014/07/paramount-martin-scorsese-silence-803900/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年3月，[[艾爾文·溫克勒|艾爾文·溫克勒]]透露，電影還在剪輯中，並確認於2016年上映。2016年8月，史柯西斯表示電影將於10月完成<ref>{{cite web|url=http://theplaylist.net/martin-scorsese-says-2016-release-silence-depends-paramount-20160805/|script-title=en:Martin Scorsese Says 2016 Release Of ‘Silence’ “Depends On Paramount”|work=[[IndieWire|The Playlist]]|first=Kevin|last=Jaugernauth|date=August 5, 2016|accessdate=August 19, 2016|archive-date=2018-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180813072855/https://theplaylist.net/martin-scorsese-says-2016-release-silence-depends-paramount-20160805/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbiz411.com/2016/08/04/oscars-martin-scorsese-says-silence-will-be-golden-for-end-of-year-release|title=Oscars: Martin Scorsese Says "Silence" Will Be Golden for End of Year Release|work=[[Showbiz411|Showbiz411]]|first=Roger|last=Friedman|date=August 4, 2016|accessdate=August 19, 2016|archive-date=2016-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820174641/http://www.showbiz411.com/2016/08/04/oscars-martin-scorsese-says-silence-will-be-golden-for-end-of-year-release|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

電影定於2016年12月23日在美國[[有限上映|有限上映]]，用以競爭熱門獎季，並於2017年1月才會廣泛上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/09/martin-scorseses-silence-paramount-1201826182/|script-title=en:Martin Scorsese’s ‘Silence’ To Open Dec. 23|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline]]|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=September 26, 2016|accessdate=September 26, 2016|archive-date=2016-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160929152645/http://deadline.com/2016/09/martin-scorseses-silence-paramount-1201826182/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該片先於2016年11月29日在[[梵蒂岡|梵蒂岡]]上首映。

派拉蒙將首支預告片於2016年11月22日在網上釋出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/watch-the-first-trailer-for-martin-scorseses-silence-1201925350/ |title=Watch the first trailer for Martin Scorsese's Silence |work=[[Variety|Variety]] |accessdate=November 23, 2016 |archive-date=2016-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161125094209/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/watch-the-first-trailer-for-martin-scorseses-silence-1201925350/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===評價===
《沉默》贏得了普遍好評。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據184條評論，新鮮度83%，平均得分7.6/10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/silence_2016/ |title=Silence (2016) |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=February 7, 2017 |archive-date=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220232653/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/silence_2016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分82（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/silence |title=Silence reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=December 14, 2016 |archive-date=2017-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170119045848/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/silence |dead-url=no }}</ref>，正面評價居多。

